Package: NECorr
Type: Package
Title: Gene Regulatory Network Correlations
Version: 0.2
Date: 2018-07-09
Authors@R: c(person("Christophe", "Liseron-Monfils", role = c("ctb"), email = "cliseron@cshl.edu"),
    person("Andrew", "Olson", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="olson@cshl.edu"))
Maintainer: Andrew Olson <olson@cshl.edu>
Description: NECorr uses molecular networks and transcriptomic data to define 
    the backbone of a biological process regulation through (NECorr-hub) 
    and putative regulator (NeECorr-Reg). 
    Implements the Gini Correlation Coefficient as in http://www.plantphysiol.org/content/160/1/192.full
